  "captions": [
    {
      "text": "Enterprises are about to launch thousands",
      "startFrame": 149,
      "endFrame": 259
    },
    {
      "text": "of AI pilots. The failure mode is not the",
      "startFrame": 260,
      "endFrame": 346
    },
    {
      "text": "demos — it is ungoverned spend with no",
      "startFrame": 347,
      "endFrame": 427
    },
    {
      "text": "proof of return. Every agent wants a",
      "startFrame": 430,
      "endFrame": 491
    },
    {
      "text": "budget, tools, and production access, but",
      "startFrame": 493,
      "endFrame": 588
    },
    {
      "text": "most teams have no investment committee",
      "startFrame": 589,
      "endFrame": 655
    },
    {
      "text": "for autonomous work. Agent IC is that",
      "startFrame": 657,
      "endFrame": 723
    },
    {
      "text": "committee. We start by giving the agent a",
      "startFrame": 724,
      "endFrame": 876
    },
    {
      "text": "safe home. NemoClaw installs a Hermes",
      "startFrame": 878,
      "endFrame": 952
    },
    {
      "text": "sandbox, scopes its network policy, and",
      "startFrame": 954,
      "endFrame": 1047
    },
    {
      "text": "names it for the Atlas Freight pilot.",
      "startFrame": 1048,
      "endFrame": 1107
    },
    {
      "text": "Hermes normalizes the raw proposal into a",
      "startFrame": 1111,
      "endFrame": 1193
    },
    {
      "text": "business, evidence, and governance schema",
      "startFrame": 1196,
      "endFrame": 1278
    },
    {
      "text": "so the agent can be reviewed like any",
      "startFrame": 1291,
      "endFrame": 1347
    },
    {
      "text": "other capital request. Agent IC evaluates",
      "startFrame": 1349,
      "endFrame": 1551
    },
    {
      "text": "the pilot the same way a CFO would.",
      "startFrame": 1552,
      "endFrame": 1622
    },
    {
      "text": "Nemotron scores usefulness, viability,",
      "startFrame": 1628,
      "endFrame": 1705
    },
    {
      "text": "risk, and ROI proof. The verdict is not a",
      "startFrame": 1714,
      "endFrame": 1789
    },
    {
      "text": "vague yes — it is Continue, with a",
      "startFrame": 1790,
      "endFrame": 1875
    },
    {
      "text": "$185,000 pilot budget, a roughly $35,000",
      "startFrame": 1879,
      "endFrame": 2043
    },
    {
      "text": "autonomous spend cap, 38-day payback, and",
      "startFrame": 2046,
      "endFrame": 2156
    },
    {
      "text": "2.36x 90-day ROI. When the agent asks to",
      "startFrame": 2157,
      "endFrame": 2279
    },
    {
      "text": "spend, Stripe authorizes a bounded",
      "startFrame": 2280,
      "endFrame": 2358
    },
    {
      "text": "checkout session with the proposal",
      "startFrame": 2361,
      "endFrame": 2420
    },
    {
      "text": "metadata and policy envelope baked in.",
      "startFrame": 2421,
      "endFrame": 2493
    },
    {
      "text": "Demo mode is safe; with a test key this",
      "startFrame": 2499,
      "endFrame": 2579
    },
    {
      "text": "becomes a real hosted Checkout Session.",
      "startFrame": 2581,
      "endFrame": 2676
    },
    {
      "text": "Funding is conditional. The pilot keeps",
      "startFrame": 2700,
      "endFrame": 2803
    },
    {
      "text": "capital only by producing evidence. We",
      "startFrame": 2805,
      "endFrame": 2879
    },
    {
      "text": "advance the ROI timeline through week two,",
      "startFrame": 2880,
      "endFrame": 2952
    },
    {
      "text": "week four, week six, and week eight. Agent",
      "startFrame": 2966,
      "endFrame": 3047
    },
    {
      "text": "IC tracks gross impact, spend consumed,",
      "startFrame": 3050,
      "endFrame": 3138
    },
    {
      "text": "net value, evidence grade, and kill",
      "startFrame": 3150,
      "endFrame": 3211
    },
    {
      "text": "criteria. At week four a weak result would",
      "startFrame": 3212,
      "endFrame": 3291
    },
    {
      "text": "trigger Kill. Here it holds. Now watch the",
      "startFrame": 3293,
      "endFrame": 3363
    },
    {
      "text": "policy envelope block an out-of-policy",
      "startFrame": 3365,
      "endFrame": 3432
    },
    {
      "text": "tool call — NemoClaw returns 403 Forbidden",
      "startFrame": 3433,
      "endFrame": 3545
    },
    {
      "text": "before any money moves. By week eight",
      "startFrame": 3550,
      "endFrame": 3731
    },
    {
      "text": "Atlas has enough proof for a",
      "startFrame": 3734,
      "endFrame": 3791
    },
    {
      "text": "finance-readable Continue decision. The",
      "startFrame": 3794,
      "endFrame": 3862
    },
    {
      "text": "committee saves a reusable Hermes playbook",
      "startFrame": 3863,
      "endFrame": 3941
    },
    {
      "text": "so the next bounded capital experiment",
      "startFrame": 3953,
      "endFrame": 4016
    },
    {
      "text": "runs the same way. This matters because",
      "startFrame": 4020,
      "endFrame": 4084
    },
    {
      "text": "agents that earn, spend, and run",
      "startFrame": 4088,
      "endFrame": 4156
    },
    {
      "text": "operations need governance, not just",
      "startFrame": 4159,
      "endFrame": 4226
    },
    {
      "text": "prompts. Agent IC runs locally with",
      "startFrame": 4228,
      "endFrame": 4304
    },
    {
      "text": "deterministic fallbacks, then upgrades to",
      "startFrame": 4306,
      "endFrame": 4386
    },
    {
      "text": "NVIDIA NIM, Hermes, and Stripe by adding",
      "startFrame": 4390,
      "endFrame": 4502
    },
    {
      "text": "environment variables. Open the live demo,",
      "startFrame": 4504,
      "endFrame": 4576
    },
    {
